column5: Headed out on Simcoe again,been a really good year for me.Just thought I would post these two beauty's to make some people drool over the amazing fishing we have on Simcoe.Only 3 weeks left till closer,get out there!!Sorry about the string in the pic!!!
nice shooting ....and welcome to the board
Beauties Welcome to OFC DeerFisher!!! Thanks for sharing Leechman
Welcome to the board. Thank you for posting those great fish pics.
